title: accessToken deep-copied into UI-facing profileList
updated_at: "2026-07-15T06:55:58Z"
---
## Problem
`syncCompactFromController` / `profileList` deep-copy includes `accessToken` (and account ids) into UI-facing property trees used by ExpandedView/compact. Tokens sit in QML properties longer than necessary and could appear in tooling/debug dumps.

## Location
contents/ui/ProfileController.qml:71-78

## Suggested fix
Keep secrets only on the controller; strip `accessToken` when building `profileList` for the view.

## Source
Review ff0a2eec Issue 12 (suggestion)